"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/90955","Cabinet Office","false","2014-09-11","<p>We will publish information on the Summer Diversity internship programme in due course.</p><p> </p>","Horsham","Mr Francis Maude","208530 ; 208562 ; 208563 ; 208564","2014-09-11T14:28:15.6232607Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/90955/answer","Biography information for Lord Maude of Horsham","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/90955/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/90955/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2014-09-08","Civil Servants: Work Experience","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, how many interns each department has accepted as part of the Summer Diversity Internship Programme; and how many such interns have been (a) women and (b) men in each year since that programme started.","false","Biography information for Gloria De Piero","Ashfield","Gloria De Piero","208565"
